  "body": "# Changelog\r\n\r\n### Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- [**breaking**] Implement `EZA_GRID_ROWS` grid details view minimum rows threshold\r\n\r\nBefore this change, the `EZA_GRID_ROWS` variable was\r\n    ignored, despite documentation existing. Users relying on `EZA_GRID_ROW`\r\n    not doing anything will find their output changed. For more info, see\r\n\r\n### Miscellaneous Tasks\r\n\r\n- Release eza v0.19.0\r\n\r\n\r\n# Checksums\r\n## sha256sum\r\n```\r\n5bbc2feede21dfcadff8cf793b759b0243c3ad9831872e926e88c85bc5d3a2f5  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.gz\r\n82c748c1873e246dbcac480adcd3b2feaf2b63d7cdd07b370a6a0041eb602425  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.zip\r\n0f36f7c606d4f1d13630d25d2c5ad799dd74b76f24e2a53d41cadb684eedc7d4  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_arm-unknown-linux-gnueabihf.tar.gz\r\nb5fd9707eead138e33ba23ea7b52ff4d7786a63af7d514adc13a530dc217b4e6  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_arm-unknown-linux-gnueabihf.zip\r\n2fa66e9b62b60419315323b234064dc6fe0f7b8e87e37b408fbdef0df501e804  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza.exe_x86_64-pc-windows-gnu.tar.gz\r\nd29801ec3cc0bb8c4d46abb46135086965c47fc038efd8e68a3edce4e4551b99  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza.exe_x86_64-pc-windows-gnu.zip\r\n21ae2106527ec6fa1caa0f4b17f028405252bd3964f770d503be08df89fe3d1c  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.gz\r\n983828ef82828c593772c00c3b2f9863d409b818dc212c4a17eeadb80e5511a4  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.zip\r\n96501b47d96d3b14542eef6569d8141a3112b3397eebe5f22717d75c055b218f  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz\r\n1b7e0863432e7a368a6503d002f1ac989da3af2f124147b5b38de9ea6794a766  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.zip\r\n```\r\n## md5sum\r\n```\r\n1b2dcee200f809519cc83093891f313c  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.gz\r\n1fc05b1d14a06b2aa98840d342721864  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.zip\r\nd2a9e6830d60406ddd0cc948feb781eb  ./target/bin-0.19.0/eza_arm-unknown-linux-gnue